sa-safe-0029,Theo Van Dinter <felicity@kluge.net>,Re: [SAtalk] Some Stupid Questions,"On Thu, Aug 22, 2002 at 01:01:44PM -0500, Ken Scott wrote:
> whitelist_from *@yahoogroups.com
> 
